These are Puzzles for 3x4 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-8-1::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: western, scientific, sports, documentary
The people have 4 different hobbies: magic-tricks, rock-climbing, sudoku, writing
There are 4 different favourite beverages: mirinda, almond-milk, juice, fanta
 1. the person who's hobby is sudoku is in an odd position##4
 2. the person watching documentary movies is on the right of the person drinking mirinda##1
 3. the person drinking juice is not to the right of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##8
 4. the person drinking mirinda is not the person watching documentary movies##6
 5. the person watching sports movies is somewhere to the right of the person watching western movies##5
 6. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
 7. the person drinking juice is not to the left of the person watching scientific movies##8
 8. the person watching scientific movies is not the person drinking fanta##6
 9. the person watching western movies is not the person who's hobby is writing##6
10. the person drinking almond-milk is the person who's hobby is writing##1
11. the person watching scientific movies is not to the right of the person drinking juice##8
12. the person watching scientific movies is in an even position##4
13. the person watching documentary movies is not to the right of the person drinking fanta##8
14. the person who's hobby is sudoku is not to the right of the person drinking juice##8

.:: Answer ::.
|         |       1       |     2      |     3      |      4       |
| Movie-Genre    | western         | documentary     | sports     | scientific         |
| Hobby   | rock-climbing | writing    | sudoku     | magic-tricks |
| Beverage   | mirinda       | almond-milk | fanta | juice       |

