.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-8-2::.
4 different pets are kept: frog, rat, horse, fish
The people have 4 different jobs:  electrician, freelancer, librarian, pilot
House: townhouse, farmhouse, victorian, cottage
 1. the librarian is not to the right of the pilot##8
 2. the owner of the horse is on the far left##1
 3. the victorian house is on the right of the townhouse house##1
 4. the owner of the fish is the freelancer##1
 5. the electrician is not the owner of the horse##6
 6. the townhouse house is on the right of the owner of the frog##1
 7. the owner of the fish is on the right of the electrician##1
 8. the owner of the frog is on the left of the owner of the fish##1
 9. the owner of the fish is somewhere to the right of the librarian##5
10. the owner of the frog is on the right of the cottage house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |      2      |     3      |     4      |
| Pet   | horse          | frog      | fish      | rat   |
| Job        | librarian     | electrician | freelancer | pilot      |
| House      | cottage | farmhouse    | townhouse  | victorian |

