.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-8-3::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: card-games, filmmaking, reading, sudoku
House: victorian, art-deco, wooden, farmhouse
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: montecristo, blend, oliveros, dunhill
 1. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the right of the dunhill-smoker##1
 2. the blend-smoker is somewhere to the right of the oliveros-smoker##5
 3. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the right of the farmhouse house##1
 4. the art-deco house is somewhere to the left of the dunhill-smoker##5
 5. the montecristo-smoker is not the victorian house##6
 6. the victorian house is on the left of the dunhill-smoker##1
 7. the victorian house is not to the right of the farmhouse house##8
 8. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the left of the wooden house##1
 9. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is in an even position##4
10. the person who's hobby is sudoku is somewhere to the left of the blend-smoker##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |   3    |     4      |
| Hobby         | reading  | filmmaking | sudoku | card-games |
| House   | art-deco  | victorian      | farmhouse | wooden        |
| Cigar     | montecristo | oliveros       | dunhill    | blend     |

