.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-8-4::.
4 different games are played: snooker, mah-jongg, bridge, domino
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: dubstep, folk, jazz, pop
There are 4 different favourite colors: azure, red, black, aquamarine
 1. the person playing mah-jongg is on the left of the fan of pop##1
 2. the person who likes red is not to the left of the fan of folk##8
 3. the fan of pop is somewhere to the right of the person playing snooker##5
 4. the person playing snooker is on the far left##1
 5. the person playing mah-jongg is not to the right of the person who likes red##8
 6. the person who likes black is not to the right of the person playing domino##8
 7. the fan of jazz is somewhere to the left of the person playing domino##5
 8. the person who likes aquamarine is somewhere to the right of the person who likes red##5
 9. the person who likes azure is on the left of the person who likes black##1
10. the person playing domino is the person who likes black##1
11. the fan of dubstep is somewhere to the right of the fan of folk##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |     3     |    4    |
| Game   | snooker   | domino | mah-jongg    | bridge |
| Music-Genre   | jazz    | folk     | dubstep   | pop     |
| Color   | azure | black   | red | aquamarine    |

