.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-8-5::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: card-games, gardening, hiking, reading
The people use 4 different means of transport: subway, train, car, trike
City: san-francisco, new-york, marseilles, colone
 1. the person who's hobby is card-games is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to new-york##5
 2. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the left of the person driving the subway##1
 3. the person driving the subway is on the far right##1
 4. the person who's hobby is reading is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is hiking##5
 5. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the right of the person driving the trike##1
 6. the person driving the trike is not the person who's hobby is hiking##6
 7. the person who's hobby is card-games is not the person traveling to marseilles##6
 8. the person driving the train is the person traveling to marseilles##1
 9. the person driving the car is not to the right of the person who's hobby is card-games##8
10. the person traveling to colone is the person who's hobby is hiking##1
11. the person traveling to colone is not to the left of the person driving the car##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2      |     3      |     4      |
| Hobby         | hiking       | card-games | gardening  | reading    |
| Transport   | car       | trike    | train | subway    |
| City         | colone | san-francisco   | marseilles   | new-york |

