The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: action, crime, documentary, horror
4 different games are played: scrabble, domino, billiard, backgammon
 1. the person drinking iced-tea is not to the left of the person watching action movies##8
 2. the person watching horror movies is not the person playing domino##6
 3. the person playing billiard is somewhere between the person drinking water and the person watching horror movies##7
 4. the person playing domino is not to the left of the person watching crime movies##8
 5. the person watching action movies is on the left or right of the person drinking fanta##3
 6. the person playing billiard is the person watching action movies##1
 7. the person drinking mirinda is somewhere to the right of the person watching documentary movies##5
 8. the person playing backgammon is between the person drinking mirinda and the person playing billiard##2
 9. the person watching horror movies is not to the right of the person drinking mirinda##8
10. the person drinking iced-tea is not to the right of the person drinking fanta##8
11. the person playing scrabble is somewhere to the left of the person watching horror movies##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |   3    |     4     |
| Beverage          | water      | iced-tea      | fanta | mirinda |
| Movie-Genre   | documentary | action    | horror | crime     |
| Game   | scrabble    | billiard | backgammon  | domino |

