There are 4 different nationalities: chinese, indonesian, malaysian, polish
The people have 4 different hobbies: fishing, rock-climbing, woodworking, cooking
 1. the person eating onion is on the right of the malaysian##1
 2. the chinese is not the person eating cauliflower##6
 3. the chinese is between the malaysian and the person who's hobby is woodworking##2
 4. the person eating cauliflower is on the right of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
 5. the person eating onion is on the left or right of the malaysian##3
 6. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the right of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
 7. the person who's hobby is woodworking is not the polish##6
 8. the person eating papaya is not to the right of the polish##8
 9. the polish is not to the left of the person who's hobby is woodworking##8
10. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is cooking##5
11. the person eating papaya is not to the left of the polish##8
12. the person eating cauliflower is not to the left of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##8
13. the person eating cauliflower is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |     3      |     4      |
| Food   | pineapple   | onion | cauliflower        | papaya |
| Nationality   | malaysian | chinese   | indonesian | polish     |
| Hobby     | cooking      | rock-climbing      | woodworking      | fishing        |

