4. the person driving the car is on the right of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
5. the person driving the taxi is not the person who's sport is snowboarding##6
6. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the left of the person driving the train##1
7. the person who's sport is snowboarding is somewhere between the person who's sport is swimming and the person who's sport is handball##7
8. the person who's sport is swimming is on the right of the person who's hobby is collecting##1
9. the person who's sport is snowboarding is the person driving the car##1

